38:56.959 --> 38:59.962
and the high winds
are carrying burning hot ash

39:00.046 --> 39:01.881
into the surrounding neighborhoods.

39:07.720 --> 39:09.305
How is this a better world?

39:17.063 --> 39:19.190
You're still seeing it with your eyes.

39:21.359 --> 39:22.693
You need to close them.

39:24.487 --> 39:26.238
Embrace the darkness.

39:34.872 --> 39:36.165
I see the future.

39:40.169 --> 39:41.170
Then tell me.

39:44.173 --> 39:45.549
Tell me my future.

39:48.803 --> 39:50.012
You come from dust.

39:52.098 --> 39:53.682
You walk the dust.

39:53.766 --> 39:55.017
You go back to dust.

39:55.768 --> 39:58.646
That's everyone's future.
Tell me my future.

39:59.522 --> 40:01.816
There is no future for you, John Dee.

40:01.899 --> 40:06.862
It is bound by walls and guards
and the sour smell of madness.

40:06.946 --> 40:10.116
And then the skein of your life is cut,
son of your mother.

40:10.825 --> 40:14.120
No. Look again. Tell me my future.

40:15.204 --> 40:18.124
You have stolen
some of the power of Dream's.

40:18.207 --> 40:20.126
You will take all of it.

40:20.209 --> 40:23.379
