I can repair the damage you have done.

41:18.392 --> 41:20.019
I'm not giving it to you, it's mine.

41:20.102 --> 41:24.273
It is harming you, John, and your world.

41:24.356 --> 41:26.025
It's revealing the truth.

41:27.776 --> 41:31.197
-This is the truth of mankind.
-No. You're wrong.

41:33.449 --> 41:35.284
This is the truth of mankind.

41:37.203 --> 41:41.749
-How's work going?
-Good, you know. Busy.

41:41.832 --> 41:43.334
They're lying to themselves.

41:44.627 --> 41:47.588
Garry's supervising a new venture
that looks promising.

41:47.671 --> 41:48.756
It's all lies.

41:48.839 --> 41:52.551
Not lies, John. Dreams.

41:52.635 --> 41:53.469
Right, sweetie?

41:53.552 --> 41:57.306
Kate dreams of running away,
where no one will find her.

41:58.432 --> 41:59.391
How are you, Bette?

42:00.267 --> 42:03.604
