42:51.652 --> 42:54.321
Then perhaps if I use it
to steal the rest of your powers,

42:54.405 --> 42:56.031
I will be the King of Dreams.

42:57.408 --> 43:02.204
If you'd rob a Dream lord of his power,
you shall do so in his realm.

43:04.748 --> 43:05.708
In dreams.

44:43.555 --> 44:45.432
Welcome home, Johnny.

44:48.352 --> 44:50.771
Don't be such a baby, Johnny.

44:58.153 --> 44:59.613
Go to sleep, Johnny.

44:59.697 --> 45:01.240
-Please.
-Mother?

45:01.323 --> 45:04.910
Johnny, you have to go to sleep.

45:08.288 --> 45:11.959
Your father was right.
I never should have had you.

45:15.587 --> 45:17.047
It's a dream!

45:18.507 --> 45:19.717
It's a dream.

45:21.760 --> 45:22.678
It's a dream.

45:50.038 --> 45:54.710
