48:51.678 --> 48:52.846
Perhaps I will.

48:55.766 --> 48:58.393
But the dream stone
was not made for mortals.

48:59.394 --> 49:01.772
And it came to you
through no fault of your own.

49:03.982 --> 49:06.944
So, no, John. I will not kill you.

49:09.863 --> 49:11.281
Sleep well, John.

49:38.850 --> 49:41.895
All the damage the ruby did,
can you undo it?

49:43.105 --> 49:44.523
