that were hidden, but never healed.

49:51.780 --> 49:54.491
Tomorrow, the rebuilding will begin.

49:56.034 --> 49:57.703
In this realm and in mine.

49:58.954 --> 50:00.205
But tonight at least…

50:02.833 --> 50:04.501
